# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository so mixed-environment
# checkouts (Windows git, WSL git, MSYS2 git in CI) agree on cleanliness -
# otherwise `git describe --dirty` reports phantom-dirty trees and release
# builds lose their clean version string.
* text=auto

# Explicit binaries
*.ico binary
*.png binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.exe binary
*.msi binary
